    NWCA 2016 Vascular Plant Taxa List

    taxaNWCA_2016.Rd

    A dataset containing taxonomy and basic characteristics for vascular plant taxa as used in NWCA 2016.

    taxaNWCA_2016

    Format

    A data frame with 5044 observations on the following 28 variables.

    SPECIES_NAME_ID

    A numeric vector containing the NWCA taxonomic ID number

    NWCA_NAME

    Accepted USDA PLANTS name, or the official NWCA name where not available

    ACCEPTED_SYMBOL

    Accepted symbol for taxon from USDA PLANTS or NWCA 2016 if not in USDA PLANTS

    TAXON_LEVEL

    Taxonomic level of name: CL (class), F (Family), G (Genus), GH (Growth habit), H (), NV (Nonvascular), SC (), SF (), SSP (Subspecies), SP (Species), T (), U (), VAR (Variety)

    DIVISION

    Division level of taxonomy

    CLASS

    Class level of taxonomy

    SUBCLASS

    Subclass level of taxonomy

    ORDER

    Order level of taxonomy

    FAMILY

    Family level of taxonomy

    GENUS

    Genus level of taxonomy

    CATEGORY

    Plant category of taxon, including MONOCOT, GYMNOSPERM, DICOT, FERN, LICHEN, HORSETAIL, MOSS, LYCOPOD, and LIVERWORT

    GROWTH_HABIT

    Growth habit of taxon as provided by USDA PLANTS

    DURATION

    Lifecycle duration of taxon as provided by USDA PLANTS

    VINE_ALL

    Indicator value for all vine types (1/0)

    HERB

    Indicator value for herbaceous vascular plant (1/0)

    SHRUB_COMB

    Indicator value for all types of shrubs (1/0)

    TREE_COMB

    Indicator value for all types of trees (1/0)

    @note This dataset is the taxa list used for state-specific CC and native status values used in NWCA 2016.
